title: Stevie Nicks - Mirror, Mirror (1985)
description:
This is the alternate original version of Stevie's "Rock A Little" album, which was originally titled "Mirror, Mirror" and contained a completely different track list. Dissatisfied with the album, Stevie scrapped a majority of these songs and recorded what we now have as "Rock A Little". Through the years, many of these songs have resurfaced as newly recorded on future albums, but these are the originals. Enjoy!

Tracklist:

1. Mirror, Mirror
2. Thousand Days
3. All The Beautiful Worlds
4. Talk To Me
5. Running Through The Garden
6. Lady From The Mountains
7. One More Big Time Rock & Roll Star
8. Battle Of The Dragon
9. Rose Garden
10. What Has Rock 'N Roll Ever Done For You?
11. Dial The Number
12. Joan Of Arc
13. Has Anyone Ever Written Anything For You?
